{"tid":2274730,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"[來回地獄又折返地獄]用緊3HK 4.5G無限想轉SoSIM","createTime":"2020-11-06T15:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T21:35:59.000Z","uid":45665,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac3b0268366442db0d24cb4b4d0fd3583caae714","tid":2274730,"uid":45665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:27:07.000Z","msg":"用緊3HK 4.5G無限就到期，look下電訊台po先知3HK原來咁多人插，平時自己用開就冇乜理有冇限速用到就算，不過斷線/連唔到網係常有<br />\n<br />\n但係見到個續約offer就火都嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Px8vFC3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPx8vFC3.jpg&h=26b04f0d&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n現時畀緊$17X/月仲包1GB大陸data(用唔用一回事)，而家咩環境仲不減反加，續就一定唔會續寧願轉台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見誠哥而家力推緊個SoSIM去望下<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.three.com.hk/prepaid/sosim/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.three.com.hk%2Fprepaid%2Fsosim%2Findex.html&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9gOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=afd8a160\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.three.com.hk/prepaid/sosim/index.html</a><br />\n仔細睇哂T&amp;C同FAQ後想轉，雖然都係用返3HK，但計返實在平好多就算垃圾都冇咁嬲<br />\n<br />\n主要考慮：<br />\n1. 本身唔係話超高用量<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uA5Nidm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuA5Nidm.jpg&h=fbf7430b&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n冇計開不過估平均每月應該唔過50GB，用開無限只係唔想煩要就住就住用<br />\n2. 3HK個號碼係以前上台新開，純data用唔係personal/work number，唔keep冇問題<br />\n3. 最concern如果轉SoSIM得返42Mbps嘅網絡表現，如果有用緊嘅巴絲請講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 近日開始認真考慮離開呢個唔係人住嘅地獄，obligation cut得就cut<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩手足畀啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9229749986c839d7927eb45aaf086561c1655795","tid":2274730,"uid":301050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"個人想轉自由鳥<br />\n我出街又唔睇片<br />\n支那移動出年先完約<br />\n一個月用唔到5GB<br />\n所以自由鳥啲plan就好啱我<br />\n樓主咪試下佢果個無限plan<br />\n話cut就cut (聽講，自己未開始用"},{"pid":"c0bd2d18fcd347bcbadeb6a69e55e165ece1551e","tid":2274730,"uid":45665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9229749986c839d7927eb45aaf086561c1655795","tid":2274730,"uid":301050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"個人想轉自由鳥<br />\n我出街又唔睇片<br />\n支那移動出年先完約<br />\n一個月用唔到5GB<br />\n所以自由鳥啲plan就好啱我<br />\n樓主咪試下佢果個無限plan<br />\n話cut就cut (聽講，自己未開始用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"自由鳥無限plan幾$/月？"},{"pid":"d971e33579b707c5640e91e7b635defa45fc1dfc","tid":2274730,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0bd2d18fcd347bcbadeb6a69e55e165ece1551e","tid":2274730,"uid":45665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9229749986c839d7927eb45aaf086561c1655795","tid":2274730,"uid":301050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"個人想轉自由鳥<br />\n我出街又唔睇片<br />\n支那移動出年先完約<br />\n一個月用唔到5GB<br />\n所以自由鳥啲plan就好啱我<br />\n樓主咪試下佢果個無限plan<br />\n話cut就cut (聽講，自己未開始用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"自由鳥無限plan幾$/月？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"好似都要2百<br />\n我淨記得90果個啱我用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26ae5f37d20944f48e38d3c0a090962783431c0","tid":2274730,"uid":13884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0bd2d18fcd347bcbadeb6a69e55e165ece1551e","tid":2274730,"uid":45665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9229749986c839d7927eb45aaf086561c1655795","tid":2274730,"uid":301050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime